entity.lycanitesmobs.aegis.name=Aegis
entity.lycanitesmobs.aegis.description=Law enforcing Order Elementals, Aegis have been known to enforce the law around villages, even petty thieves will be mercilessly pursued.
entity.lycanitesmobs.aegis.habitat=Being Order Elementals, Aegis manifest in areas rich in the Order element, thus villages very commonly create these creatures.
